OL,3,CMan, 22, arrested after alleged rape
OL,4,Cof teenage girl in Bristol
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof raping a teenage girl in Bristol.
OL,9,FAvon and Somerset Police said they are
OL,10,Finvestigating a serious sexual assault
OL,11,Fon "a child in her mid-teens", that
OL,12,Fhappened in the Portland Square area
OL,13,Fon Saturday 20 June.
OL,15,FThey said the alleged assault took
OL,16,Fplace at around 3.30am and the victim
OL,17,Fhas been offered access to any support
OL,18,Fservices she feels she would benefit
OL,19,Ffrom.
