OL,3,CMan, 22, arrested after alleged rape
OL,4,Cof teenage girl in Bristol
OL,6,FOfficers checked CCTV footage and
OL,7,Fappealed to the public for information
OL,8,Fearlier this week. Yesterday they
OL,9,Farrested a 22-year-old man on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of rape.
OL,12,FAnybody with information that could
OL,13,Fassist the investigation is asked to
OL,14,Fcall 101 quoting reference 5226169935
OL,15,For complete the appeals form on the
OL,16,Fpolice website.
